briefdescription.para: Read the contents of one array buffer to another.

detaileddescription.para: This safe version doesn't use Unsafe, and may be up to 3x slower than ReadArrayOutUnsafe().

parameterdescription.para: Source array to copy from.
Bit position in source to start reading frome.
Target array
Current write position for target. Will start writing at this bitposition. Value gets incremented.
Number of bits to readout. Typically the current write position of the source buffer.
